<p>Thunderbolt booting, repair pricing/strategies, unreliable Apple TV connections, Skype microphone recommendations and monitors that make your Mac crash. All of this and more in this week&#39;s episode of Mac Geek Gab. Have a question or tip of your own? Send it in and your two favorite geeks will cover it!</p>
